                    </h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Scope of Services:</b> The package scope is limited strictly to the number of universities and services explicitly stated in the selected package. Any additional universities or services requested will be billed separately.</li>
                        <li><b>Timelines & Client Responsibility:</b> Service timelines are dependent on the client’s responsiveness, timely submission of complete documents, and official university deadlines. SureAdmit shall not be held responsible for delays resulting from late, incomplete, or inaccurate information provided by the client.</li>
                        <li><b>Document Revisions:</b> Document-related services include reasonable revisions within the agreed scope. Significant changes to academic focus, research direction, career goals, or applicant profile after work has commenced may require additional fees.</li>
                        <li><b>No Guarantee of Outcomes:</b> University shortlisting, advisory, and application support are consultative and process-driven services. SureAdmit does not guarantee admission offers, scholarships, funding, visa approvals, or processing timelines.</li>
                        <li><b>Excluded Costs:</b> University application fees, standardized test fees, credential evaluations (e.g., WES), courier charges, visa fees, and any third-party costs are not included, unless explicitly stated in writing.</li>
                        <li><b>Payment Terms:</b> All fees are payable in advance, either in full or as per mutually agreed milestones, and must be received before the commencement of services.</li>
                        <li><b>Non-Refundable Fees:</b> All payments are non-refundable and non-transferable once services have commenced, as services involve time-bound intellectual, advisory, and strategic work.</li>
                        <li><b>Service Initiation Exception:</b> In the unlikely event that SureAdmit does not initiate services within seven (7) business days of receiving payment, a pro-rata refund may be considered at management’s sole discretion.</li>
                        <li><b>Limitation of Liability:</b> No refunds or claims shall be applicable for delays, rejections, or outcomes beyond SureAdmit’s control, including decisions made by universities, testing agencies, credential evaluators, or immigration authorities.</li>
                        <li>All payments made in Indian currency will attract additional GST Charges @@18%</li>
                    </ul>
